service.name: Health Care Card (FTB)
service.description: Health Care Card (FTB) (HCC FTB) is a  card generally issued to customers eligible for the maximum rate of income tested FTB Part A. A customer's (HCC) includes any dependent children of the customer (and their partner if applicable) aged under 16 years of age and any dependent full-time secondary students aged 16-18 years.
